<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Resend OTP</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div
    style="
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
    "
  >
    <h2 style="color: #007bff;">OTP Resent Successfully</h2>

    <p>Hello <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>

    <p>
      As requested, we’ve resent your One-Time Password (OTP) to help you
      continue the verification process.
    </p>

    <p>Please use the OTP below to verify your email address:</p>

    <div
      style="
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #dc3545;
        margin: 20px 0;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
      "
    >
      <%= otp %>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Note:</strong> This OTP is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>

    <p>
      For your security, please do not share this OTP with anyone.
      If you did not request this OTP, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br />
      <strong>The Team</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
